    AfuMktConstants

    Constant (static final) methods for Mkt functions

    This method must be updated when changing the Enumerated.xml, C header files, and enumerates at .dat files. See the information above each one to know more
    Author:
    Asier SAMPIETRO 20/Jul/2017
